PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1782402488
OL,3,CSchools shut early due to extreme heat
OL,4,Cas temperatures may hit 40 degrees
OL,6,FSeveral Channel Island schools closed
OL,7,Fearly on Monday due to the extreme
OL,8,Fheat, with further announcements
OL,9,Fexpected over the coming days as
OL,10,Ftemperatures continue to climb.
OL,12,FGrainville School in St Saviour
OL,13,Finformed parents that students would
OL,14,Fbe sent home at 1:10pm, with buses
OL,15,Fprovided to town and the students'
OL,16,Fhome parishes.
OL,18,FSt Helier's all-boys Victoria College
OL,19,Fwill finish at 1pm between Monday and
OL,20,FWednesday and children have been
OL,21,Fencouraged to wear a PE kit to classes.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
