FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1782402488
OL,3,CSchools shut early due to extreme heat
OL,4,Cas temperatures may hit 40 degrees
OL,6,FIt comes as the head of Jersey Met,
OL,7,FPaul Aked, says the islands could
OL,8,Frecord their hottest-ever day this
OL,9,Fweek.
OL,11,FHe explains: "We're seeing some very
OL,12,Fhigh temperatures for Jersey and
OL,13,Facross the Channel Islands. Our
OL,14,Fwarmest recorded temperature in Jersey
OL,15,Fis 37.9 and we could see that record
OL,16,Fbroken this week.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1782402488
OL,3,CSchools shut early due to extreme heat
OL,4,Cas temperatures may hit 40 degrees
OL,6,F"We're expecting the peak of the heat
OL,7,Fon Tuesday and Wednesday, with
OL,8,Ftemperatures in the high 30s. Although
OL,9,Funlikely, we can't rule out that
OL,10,Ftemperature reaching 40 degrees.
OL,12,F"Guernsey is a couple of degrees
OL,13,Fcooler but across the islands, we
OL,14,Fcould still see records fall."
OL,16,FMeanwhile, in a post on social media,
OL,17,Fthe headteacher of St Helier's Haute
OL,18,FVallee School, Stuart Hughes, says
OL,19,Fthat he is monitoring the situation
OL,20,Fand what is safe for students.
OL,26,@zD@Err
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1782402488
OL,3,CSchools shut early due to extreme heat
OL,4,Cas temperatures may hit 40 degrees
OL,6,FHe explains: "I do not want to close
OL,7,Fdue to warmer weather but if I feel
OL,8,Fthat making this decision is
OL,9,Fappropriate, because the temperatures
OL,10,Fare unmanageable, I will give parents
OL,11,Fas much notice as possible.
OL,13,F"I will also ensure that those
OL,14,Fstudents who cannot be released early,
OL,15,Ffor various reasons, are supported
OL,16,Funtil the end of the school day."
OL,18,FMr Hughes also asked students to wear
OL,19,Ftheir summer uniform, adding that they
OL,20,Fcan leave blazers, ties and PE
OL,21,Ftracksuits at home.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
